<div class="container op-container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <img class="op-avatar" src="profile_pic.jpg" alt="Profile photo">
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      Engineer, creator, dreamer
      <hr />
      <h3>Bio</h3>
      <p>
        Software engineer in retail supply chain. University of Washington, class of 2018. #Husky
